<?xml encoding="ISO-8859-1" ?>

<sect1 id="installation-haskell">
 <title>Haskell</title>

 <indexterm>
  <primary>Haskell</primary>
  <secondary>installation</secondary>
 </indexterm>

 <para>
  For at komme i gang med at programmere i Haskell på Linux skal du blot
  installere en Haskell-oversætter eller fortolker.

 </para>

 <sect2 id="installation-haskell-rpm">
  <title>På RPM-baserede systemer</title>

  <para>
   Du kan hente RPM-pakker med Haskell-fortolkeren Hugs på <ulink
   url="http://www.cse.ogi.edu/PacSoft/projects/Hugs/pages/downloading.htm#Linux">http://www.cse.ogi.edu/PacSoft/projects/Hugs/pages/downloading.htm#Linux</ulink>.
  </para>
 </sect2>

 <sect2 id="installation-haskell-deb">
  <title>På Debian-baserede systemer</title>

  <para>
   <command>apt-get update &amp;&amp; apt-get install hugs hugs-doc</command> skulle
   klare det. Ellers kan du hente kildeteksten på <ulink
   url="http://www.cse.ogi.edu/PacSoft/projects/Hugs/pages/downloading.htm">http://www.cse.ogi.edu/PacSoft/projects/Hugs/pages/downloading.htm</ulink>.
  </para>
 </sect2>
</sect1>
